### Device Register - Create new device
POST http://localhost:8080/device-register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "abc123def456ghi789",
  "installationId": "inst9876543210abc",
  "platform": "android",
  "appVersion": "1.2.3",
  "buildNumber": "45",
  "packageName": "com.guardian.vpn",
  "timezone": "America/Sao_Paulo",
  "language": "pt-BR",
  "timestamp": {{$timestamp}}
}

### Device Register - Update existing device
POST http://localhost:8080/device-register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "abc123def456ghi789",
  "installationId": "inst9876543210abc",
  "platform": "android",
  "appVersion": "1.2.4",
  "buildNumber": "46",
  "packageName": "com.guardian.vpn",
  "timezone": "America/Sao_Paulo",
  "language": "en-US",
  "timestamp": {{$timestamp}}
}

### Device Register - Invalid deviceId (too short)
POST http://localhost:8080/device-register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "short",
  "installationId": "inst9876543210abc",
  "platform": "android",
  "appVersion": "1.0",
  "buildNumber": "1",
  "timestamp": {{$timestamp}}
}

### Device Register - Invalid platform
POST http://localhost:8080/device-register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "abc123def456ghi789",
  "installationId": "inst9876543210abc",
  "platform": "ios",
  "appVersion": "1.0",
  "buildNumber": "1",
  "timestamp": {{$timestamp}}
}

### Device Register - Missing required fields
POST http://localhost:8080/device-register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceId": "abc123def456ghi789"
}
